title: Day 1193
content:
# Day 1193

Dear Heavenly Father,

Please give me the agency to do the things I know I can do. The courage to stand up for what is right, to lead my household, and to do the right thing - not the easy thing, when faced with hard choices. Give me the discipline to craft a strong body, a bright mind, and keep a sense of calm and peace when others provoke me. Finally, I ask for Your Grace when I fall short.

In Jesus name I pray.

Amen.

6/27/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
